    <item>
      <title>期权定价表明卢比可能进一步贬值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/options-pricing-suggests-rupee-is-likely-to-weaken-further</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卢比短期内将从历史低点延续跌势，期权市场预示，到 3 月底，卢比兑美元汇率很有可能跌至 87。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/options-pricing-suggests-rupee-is-likely-to-weaken-further</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 02:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳元交易员加大看跌押注，预计 2022 年将跌至低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/aussie-dollar-traders-ramp-up-bearish-bets-with-2022-low-in-view</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着经济数据走弱且美国上调关税的可能性加大，交易员们越来越多地预计澳元将跌至 2020 年以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/aussie-dollar-traders-ramp-up-bearish-bets-with-2022-low-in-view</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 01:58:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受特朗普冲击的菲律宾股市因支出和利润反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/trump-hit-philippine-stocks-seen-rebounding-on-spending-profits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾股市在经历了唐纳德·特朗普赢得大选以来亚洲最大幅度的下跌后，有望出现转机，而国内支出增加预计将推高盈利。]]></description>
