      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 01:33:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济低迷加剧 中国人民银行暂停债券购买以捍卫人民币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/pboc-says-it-will-temporarily-halt-buying-of-government-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行宣布将暂停购买国债，这是央行为抑制投资者对经济增长乏力的押注而做出的最新尝试。经济增长乏力已压低人民币汇率，并削弱了企业和消费者的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/pboc-says-it-will-temporarily-halt-buying-of-government-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 01:10:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国掉期曲线反转，因交易员减少降息押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/china-swap-curve-inverts-as-traders-dial-back-rate-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国货币市场押注当局将推迟预期的货币宽松措施，以支持陷入困境的人民币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/china-swap-curve-inverts-as-traders-dial-back-rate-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 00:33:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场收紧，油价创 7 月以来最长周度涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-10</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价连续第三周上涨，有望创下 7 月份以来的最佳涨幅，因美国库存下降等市场吃紧迹象抵消了对最大进口国中国需求疲软的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-10</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 23:30:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
