    <item>
      <title>优衣库母公司受中国业务担忧影响 5 个月来股价跌幅最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/uniqlo-owner-reports-strong-growth-in-japan-western-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心大中华区销售额下降，优衣库母公司迅销集团 (Fast Retailing Co.) 的股价出现五个月来最大跌幅，而大中华区占该公司营业利润的三分之一以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/uniqlo-owner-reports-strong-growth-in-japan-western-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 06:54:30 GMT</pubDate>
